{"type":"message","id":"65bdccf6","parentId":"c5ff3d1f","timestamp":"2026-02-10T03:12:20.179Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me create today's memory file documenting this work.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"c89e9217-06dd-4051-93ff-2969eed7e6b6","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-02-10.md","content":"# 2026-02-10 - Skills Inventory Complete\n\n## Task: Catalog Project Skills\n\nScanned and inventorized 115 skills from `/home/project/openclaw/skills/`.\n\n### Created Artifacts\n\n1. **Catalog**: `memory/skills-catalog.json`\n   - Full JSON inventory with categories, subcategories, purposes\n   - Use-case keyword mapping (send_email → gmail-automation, etc.)\n   - Skill index for fast lookup\n\n2. **Search Script**: `scripts/skill-search.py`\n   - `skill-search.py <query>` — keyword search\n   - `skill-search.py --recommend \"<task>\"` — task-based recommendations\n   - `skill-search.py --category <cat>` — list by category\n   - `skill-search.py --use-case <uc>` — find by use case\n   - `skill-search.py --detail <skill>` — show SKILL.md preview\n   - `skill-search.py --list` — show all categories\n\n### Skill Categories (9 total)\n\n| Category | Count | Description |\n|----------|-------|-------------|\n| app_automation | 78 | SaaS apps via Rube MCP (Composio) |\n| development | 11 | Coding, DevOps, development tools |\n| creative_media | 6 | Design, visual art, media |\n| business_marketing | 5 | Sales, marketing, BI |\n| productivity | 5 | Organization, workflow |\n| communication_writing | 2 | Content creation |\n| meta_utility | 5 | Skill creation, app connections |\n| finance | 1 | Financial data |\n| messaging | 1 | Messaging integrations |\n\n### Key Insights\n\n- **App Automation** skills require Rube MCP (`https://rube.app/mcp`) and OAuth via `RUBE_MANAGE_CONNECTIONS`\n- Most automation skills follow pattern: search tools first, then manage connections, then execute\n- Development skills have scripts/ directories for automation\n- Use-case mapping makes task→skill matching easier\n\n### Updated Files\n\n- `TOOLS.md` — Added skill search reference and quick lookup table\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":823,"output":496,"cacheRead":46720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48039,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1770693107082}}
