{"type":"message","id":"812f773a","parentId":"f5b44890","timestamp":"2026-02-10T03:12:44.700Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great! Now let me provide a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## ✅ Skills Inventory Complete\n\nI've built a complete catalog system for the **115 skills** in `/home/project/openclaw/skills/`:\n\n### 📦 Created Artifacts\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `memory/skills-catalog.json` | Full JSON catalog with categories, purposes, use-case mapping |\n| `scripts/skill-search.py` | Search tool to find skills by keyword, task, or category |\n\n### 🔍 Search Script Usage\n\n```bash\n# Find skills for a task\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill-search.py --recommend \"send email to customer\"\n\n# Search by keyword\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill-search.py \"stripe\"\n\n# List by category\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill-search.py --category development\n\n# Show skill details\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill-search.py --detail mcp-builder\n\n# List all categories\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill-search.py --list\n```\n\n### 📊 Skills Breakdown\n\n| Category | Count | What It Does |\n|----------|-------|--------------|\n| **App Automation** | 78 | SaaS apps via Composio (Gmail, Slack, GitHub, Stripe, etc.) |\n| **Development** | 11 | MCP builder, artifacts, webapp testing, changelogs |\n| **Creative/Media** | 6 | Canvas design, image enhance, video download, themes |\n| **Business** | 5 | Lead research, competitive ads, Twitter optimizer |\n| **Productivity** | 5 | File organizer, invoice organizer, resume generator |\n| **Meta/Utility** | 5 | Skill creator, connect apps, templates |\n\n### 🎯 How I'll Use This\n\nWhen you give me a task, I can now:\n1. **Quick search**: `skill-search.py --recommend \"your task\"` → get ranked suggestions\n2. **Use-case lookup**: Match tasks to pre-defined use cases (send_email, create_issue, etc.)\n3. **Category browsing**: Filter by category when you know the domain\n4. **Detail view**: Read the actual SKILL.md for implementation details\n\nUpdated `TOOLS.md` with the quick reference and search commands. 🧩"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":48051,"output":504,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48555,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770693140189}}
