{"type":"message","id":"0f33b047","parentId":"4d521af0","timestamp":"2026-02-11T01:25:16.787Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"cd48ae5f-99a3-482a-8021-947d1702a355","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Memory - 2026-02-09\n\n## Project Folder Scan: `/home/project/openclaw/`\n\n### Overview\nThis is the primary OpenClaw project workspace with multiple active components.\n\n### Directory Structure\n```\n/home/project/openclaw/\n├── skills/              # Custom skills for OpenClaw\n│   ├── chrome-devtools-mcp/        # Design extraction via Chrome DevTools MCP\n│   ├── opencode-orchestrator/      # Autonomous coding task orchestration\n│   ├── playwright-design-extractor/ # Website design extraction (headless)\n│   ├── slack/                      # Slack integration\n│   └── yahoo-finance/              # Yahoo Finance data fetching\n├── logs/                # Daily ping logs (daily-ping-YYYY-MM-DD.log)\n├── design-extraction-playwright/  # Playwright design extraction tests\n├── design-extraction-test/        # Design extraction test files\n├── extraction/        # Extraction output\n├── synthesis/         # Synthesis output\n├── tests/             # Test files\n└── node_modules/      # Node dependencies\n```\n\n### Key Files\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| WORKSPACE_CONFIG.md | Workspace configuration, agent paths, skills registry |\n| TOOLS.md | Local configuration for workspace and coding agents |\n| HEARTBEAT.md | Periodic tasks: S&P 500 monitor, daily ping |\n| daily-ping-config.md | Daily ping schedule and configuration |\n| PYTHON_DEV_RULES.md | Python development guidelines |\n| Meticulous_Approach.md | SOP documentation |\n| AGENTS.md | Agent workspace protocol |\n| config.txt | OpenClaw configuration (models, plugins, gateway) |\n\n### Active Automation\n1. **Daily Ping** (7:00 AM SGT via cron)\n   - Bitcoin price from CoinGecko\n   - Stocks: NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD\n   - GitHub trending repos\n   - Delivered via Telegram to @PC188\n\n2. **S&P 500 Volatility Monitor** (Every 30 min heartbeat)\n   - Alerts if S&P 500 drops ≥10%\n   - Logs to spx_monitor.log\n\n### Coding Agents (Configured)\n| Agent | Path | Purpose |\n|-------|------|---------|\n| OpenCode | `/usr/bin/opencode` | General coding, full-stack |\n| Kimi CLI | `/home/pete/.local/bin/kimi-cli` | Code analysis, debugging |\n| Gemini | `/usr/bin/gemini` | Quick Q&A, summaries |\n\n### Model Configuration\n- Primary: Kimi K2.5 (via NVIDIA API)\n- Fallbacks: GPT-5.2, Claude Sonnet 4.5, Gemini 3 Flash, Grok 4\n\n### Enabled Plugins\n- WhatsApp ✅\n- Telegram ✅\n- Discord ✅\n- Slack ✅\n- Google Chat ✅\n- Nostr ✅\n\n### User Contacts\n- Primary: +6591127357\n- Backup: +6597730111\n\n### Protocol\n- Task completion: Send WhatsApp summary to +6597730111\n\n---\n\n## Session Notes\n\n### 2026-02-09 Afternoon\n- User requested project folder scan\n- Documented `/home/project/openclaw/` structure\n- Recorded workspace configuration in memory\n- Fixed missing `yfinance` package, ran daily ping manually\n- **NEW:** Discovered 11 Knowledge Work Plugins at `/home/project/openclaw/knowledge-work-plugins/`\n  - 55 total skills across domains: bio-research, customer-support, data, enterprise-search, finance, legal, marketing, product-management, productivity, sales\n  - 42 slash commands available\n  - Full inventory saved to `memory/knowledge-work-plugins-inventory.md`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1770773116778}}
