{"type":"message","id":"25144d60","parentId":"f205a71d","timestamp":"2026-02-11T01:26:15.527Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"2029a472-e661-4477-aad9-c838341830e0","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Daily Ping Configuration\n\n**Status:** Pending API configuration\n\n## Schedule\n- **Time:** 7:00 AM SGT (Singapore Time, GMT+8)\n- **Cron Expression:** `0 23 * * *` (11:00 PM UTC = 7:00 AM SGT next day)\n- **Delivery:** Telegram (@PC188)\n\n## Task Components\n\n### 1. GitHub Trending Repositories\n- **Source:** https://github.com/trending\n- **Count:** Top 5 repositories\n- **Blocker:** Page requires JavaScript, blocks scraping\n\n### 2. Bitcoin Price Monitor\n- **Source:** https://www.coinbase.com/en-sg/price/bitcoin\n- **Alert Trigger:** Price drop > 10%\n- **Blocker:** Cloudflare protection (403 error)\n\n## Solutions Required\n\n### Option A: Brave Search API\n```bash\nopenclaw configure --section web\n# Add BRAVE_API_KEY\n```\n\n### Option B: Alternative APIs\n- **Crypto:** CoinGecko API (free tier available)\n- **GitHub:** GitHub Search API (trending not officially supported)\n\n### Option C: Manual Mode\nUser requests daily summary manually\n\n## Implementation\n\n### Current Status\n- ✅ Shell script created: `/home/project/openclaw/daily-ping-cron.sh`\n- ✅ Data sources working (CoinGecko API, GitHub API)\n- ⚠️ OpenClaw cron tool configuration pending\n\n### Manual Setup Required\n```bash\n# Add to system crontab for 7am SGT daily\ncrontab -e\n# Add: 0 23 * * * /home/project/openclaw/daily-ping-cron.sh\n```\n\n### Data Sources\n- **Bitcoin:** CoinGecko API (free, no key required) — Primary\n- **GitHub:** GitHub Search API (top starred repos) — Primary\n- **Stocks:** Yahoo Finance (NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD) — Primary\n- **Backup/Fallback:** Brave Search API (configured, rate limited to 1 req/sec)\n\n### Rate Limits\n- **Brave Search Free Plan:** 1 request per second, 2000 queries/month\n- **CoinGecko:** 10-30 calls/minute on free tier\n- **GitHub API:** 60 requests/hour unauthenticated\n\n### Message Delivery\n- **Method:** HEARTBEAT.md trigger (not direct cron)\n- **Timing:** ~7:05 AM SGT (after data collection)\n- **Process:** Heartbeat checks log file → Formats message → Sends via Telegram\n- **Tracking:** `last-daily-ping-sent.txt` prevents duplicates\n\n### Note\nTrue \"trending\" repos require scraping GitHub's trending page (no official API). Current implementation shows most-starred repositories. Use Brave Search as fallback for additional context when needed.\n\n**Created:** 2026-02-02\n**Last Updated:** 2026-02-02"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":32,"aggregated":"# Daily Ping Configuration\n\n**Status:** Pending API configuration\n\n## Schedule\n- **Time:** 7:00 AM SGT (Singapore Time, GMT+8)\n- **Cron Expression:** `0 23 * * *` (11:00 PM UTC = 7:00 AM SGT next day)\n- **Delivery:** Telegram (@PC188)\n\n## Task Components\n\n### 1. GitHub Trending Repositories\n- **Source:** https://github.com/trending\n- **Count:** Top 5 repositories\n- **Blocker:** Page requires JavaScript, blocks scraping\n\n### 2. Bitcoin Price Monitor\n- **Source:** https://www.coinbase.com/en-sg/price/bitcoin\n- **Alert Trigger:** Price drop > 10%\n- **Blocker:** Cloudflare protection (403 error)\n\n## Solutions Required\n\n### Option A: Brave Search API\n```bash\nopenclaw configure --section web\n# Add BRAVE_API_KEY\n```\n\n### Option B: Alternative APIs\n- **Crypto:** CoinGecko API (free tier available)\n- **GitHub:** GitHub Search API (trending not officially supported)\n\n### Option C: Manual Mode\nUser requests daily summary manually\n\n## Implementation\n\n### Current Status\n- ✅ Shell script created: `/home/project/openclaw/daily-ping-cron.sh`\n- ✅ Data sources working (CoinGecko API, GitHub API)\n- ⚠️ OpenClaw cron tool configuration pending\n\n### Manual Setup Required\n```bash\n# Add to system crontab for 7am SGT daily\ncrontab -e\n# Add: 0 23 * * * /home/project/openclaw/daily-ping-cron.sh\n```\n\n### Data Sources\n- **Bitcoin:** CoinGecko API (free, no key required) — Primary\n- **GitHub:** GitHub Search API (top starred repos) — Primary\n- **Stocks:** Yahoo Finance (NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD) — Primary\n- **Backup/Fallback:** Brave Search API (configured, rate limited to 1 req/sec)\n\n### Rate Limits\n- **Brave Search Free Plan:** 1 request per second, 2000 queries/month\n- **CoinGecko:** 10-30 calls/minute on free tier\n- **GitHub API:** 60 requests/hour unauthenticated\n\n### Message Delivery\n- **Method:** HEARTBEAT.md trigger (not direct cron)\n- **Timing:** ~7:05 AM SGT (after data collection)\n- **Process:** Heartbeat checks log file → Formats message → Sends via Telegram\n- **Tracking:** `last-daily-ping-sent.txt` prevents duplicates\n\n### Note\nTrue \"trending\" repos require scraping GitHub's trending page (no official API). Current implementation shows most-starred repositories. Use Brave Search as fallback for additional context when needed.\n\n**Created:** 2026-02-02\n**Last Updated:** 2026-02-02","cwd":"/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1770773175517}}
