{"type":"message","id":"cea53f06","parentId":"964ca3fc","timestamp":"2026-02-11T01:27:54.014Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script exists and there are logs from previous runs. The last log was on 2026-02-09, but nothing from today (2026-02-11). Looking at the dates, it seems like the cron job was set up via system crontab at some point, but either:\n1. It was removed\n2. The system was rebooted\n3. The cron daemon isn't running\n\nLet me check the system crontab and also set up the job via OpenClaw's cron tool.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"The script exists and worked before (last run Feb 9). The system cron job must have been removed. Let me check and recreate it:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"210346b3-02a9-423e-b738-aed0800e90fb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"crontab -l 2>/dev/null || echo \"No crontab configured\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"0d02dcea-3930-4c85-91ce-91221a765fe9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /etc/cron.d/openclaw 2>/dev/null || echo \"No /etc/cron.d/openclaw\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":49181,"output":302,"cacheRead":3904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53387,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1770773248517}}
