{"type":"message","id":"4f3bf781","parentId":"9b5f4a12","timestamp":"2026-02-11T01:29:19.613Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the system cron is set up. Now let me also create an OpenClaw cron job that will send the daily summary message via the agent. This will be a backup in case the system cron fails, or we can use it as the primary method.\n\nFor the OpenClaw cron job, I need to create an agentTurn job that:\n1. Fetches Bitcoin, stocks, and GitHub data\n2. Formats a message\n3. Sends it to Telegram\n\nThe schedule should be `0 23 * * *` (11pm UTC = 7am SGT) with timezone Asia/Singapore.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"System cron is set up. Now let me also create an OpenClaw cron job as backup that sends directly:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"565c746f-bab2-4e64-b57c-b6c384776b8c","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"daily-ping-telegram","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 7 * * *","tz":"Asia/Singapore"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Send the daily ping to Telegram (@PC188). Fetch: 1) Bitcoin price from CoinGecko API (https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin&vs_currencies=usd&include_24hr_change=true), 2) Stock prices for NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD using yfinance, 3) Top 5 GitHub repos by stars (https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=stars:>1000&sort=stars&order=desc&per_page=5). Format as a concise morning summary with emoji and send via message tool to Telegram target @PC188.","thinking":"low","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"enabled":true}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":5305,"output":516,"cacheRead":48640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54461,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1770773342687}}
{"type":"message","id":"91419aa1","parentId":"4f3bf781","timestamp":"2026-02-11T01:29:19.661Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"565c746f-bab2-4e64-b57c-b6c384776b8c","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"10a19bb7-7afb-4b24-8478-62555b540c2d\",\n  \"agentId\": \"main\",\n  \"name\": \"daily-ping-telegram\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1770773359648,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1770773359648,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 7 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Singapore\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"Send the daily ping to Telegram (@PC188). Fetch: 1) Bitcoin price from CoinGecko API (https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin&vs_currencies=usd&include_24hr_change=true), 2) Stock prices for NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD using yfinance, 3) Top 5 GitHub repos by stars (https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=stars:>1000&sort=stars&order=desc&per_page=5). Format as a concise morning summary with emoji and send via message tool to Telegram target @PC188.\",\n    \"thinking\": \"low\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"none\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1770850800000\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"10a19bb7-7afb-4b24-8478-62555b540c2d","agentId":"main","name":"daily-ping-telegram","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1770773359648,"updatedAtMs":1770773359648,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 7 * * *","tz":"Asia/Singapore"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Send the daily ping to Telegram (@PC188). Fetch: 1) Bitcoin price from CoinGecko API (https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin&vs_currencies=usd&include_24hr_change=true), 2) Stock prices for NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD using yfinance, 3) Top 5 GitHub repos by stars (https://api.github.com/search/reposito