{"type":"message","id":"65aae900","parentId":"3c196b7b","timestamp":"2026-02-11T01:29:47.933Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron job is set up. The next run will be tomorrow (Feb 12) at 7:00 AM SGT. Let me explain to the user what happened and what I fixed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🔧 Fixed!\n\n**What happened:** The system crontab was never configured - the script existed but no cron job was running it.\n\n**What I did:**\n\n| Layer | Status | Next Run |\n|-------|--------|----------|\n| **System cron** | ✅ Added | Tomorrow 7:00 AM SGT |\n| **OpenClaw cron** | ✅ Created | Tomorrow 7:00 AM SGT |\n\nNow you have **two layers of backup**:\n1. **System cron** runs the shell script (`daily-ping-cron.sh`) at 23:00 UTC (7am SGT)\n2. **OpenClaw cron** will also send the daily summary at 7:00 AM SGT directly\n\nThe OpenClaw job will run **tomorrow (Feb 12) at 7:00 AM SGT** - you should get your morning ping with:\n- 📊 Bitcoin price (CoinGecko)\n- 📈 Stocks: NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD\n- ⭐ Top 5 GitHub repos\n\nWant me to run a test ping right now to verify everything works?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":51328,"output":322,"cacheRead":3840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55490,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770773366791}}
